  "body": "**üßê Motivation**\r\n\r\nAn RLP library is needed when transactions need to be encoded and hashed on-chain. This is especially relevant in the context of layer 2 solutions. Having an RLP library part of the contracts library would extend its utility toolkit for such projects.\r\n\r\n**üìù Details**\r\n\r\nImplement an RLP library that supports the encoding of most common Solidity types and lists as well as decoding of RLP encoded elements.",
